* Inkscape 0.48: Vector Grafik\\
[[http://inkscape.org/download/|Windows and Mac]] / For Linux use your distribution's packages (we will provide binaries for Debian testing) ([[https://bugs.launchpad.net/inkscape/+bug/482993/comments/59|Patch]] für Snow Leopard)
* Gimp 2.6: Bildbearbeitung\\
[[http://downloads.sourceforge.net/gimp-win/gimp-2.6.11-i686-setup-1.exe|Windows]] / [[http://gimp.lisanet.de/Website/Download.html|Mac]] / For Linux use your distribution's packages
* Mypaint 0.9: Computermalerei\\
[[http://download.gna.org/mypaint/mypaint-0.9.0-win32-installer.exe|Windows]] / For Linux we will try to provide binaries
* OpenOffice.org\\
[[http://download.openoffice.org|Windows and Mac]] / For Linux use your distribution's packages

